features: 12 PCS Number Train: Wooden train set with bright color consists of 11 pcs number and 1 pcs train head, every train body is individual and connected by magnets. Each train has 4 sliding wheels which glide easily.

Great Preschool Educational Toy: Toddlers not only learn simple number by combing digtal trains but also play trains with friends. These number car help kids to study digtal, promote imagination, hand-eye coordination, fine motor skills, basic cognitive skills, problem-solving, color recognition, visual perception.

Safe And High Quality: Wooden train set made of high quality natural wood material and 100% non-toxic paints, sturdy wooden construction, round edges with no sharp, lightweight and harmless. Fully tested to the highest ASTM and CPSIA toy safety standards, safe for children to play.

Stronger Magnet: The magnets on our wooden trains were carefully chosen and have been tested extensively to be stronger than those in other sets. This means more train cars can be connected together to make longer trains. 12 pcs wooden train set compatible with other track toys.

Fun STEM Games: Toddlers learn through play wooden number train set, communication the most important people around them, playing with your child, It’s a great interaction between for parents and children, very helpful for kids growth. It is a nice gift idea for Birthday, Christmas, Thanksgiving or any other suitable occasion.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 31, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Sturdy wood pieces. Love the bucket they come in. They had space to add other wooden pieces we already had. My son loves them. They can create a long train without the magnets breaking chain. Only complaint is the small paint chips disbursed in the box upon first opening.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 10, 2023
reviews.reviewText: My nephew loved these! they are great quality and have a very good magnet, if your child loves trains they will love these. Great christmas or birthday gift!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Best toy I’ve bought in a long time
reviews.reviewText: Sturdy little wooden toy letters with chip resistant paint and smooth wheels. When all the cars are linked together, they are strong enough to pull the whole alphabet. The best thing about this toy is that they’re magnet so if the letter is backwards then it won’t stick together so then the child will learn the proper direction of the letters. My son has started throwing the cars and they still look amazing. The quality of this toy is commendable. They also come in a cute container to house the toy when not in use. Perfect for a gift or for your littles.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Adorable but magnet doesn’t pull train
reviews.reviewText: Attached by magnet. But when my child pulled the train, it always broke apart. Magnets not strong enough to hold all 26 letters as a train should. But he played with it for hours… so 4 stars.
